msgctxt "talk12"
msgid ""
"<1.so>A strange place, huh... <2.pa>That could mean\n"
"a lot of... Oh, wait! Are you talking about\n"
"our resident Mr. Toothy?<3.pa>\n"
"I mean, <4.pa>his shop's not called that.<5.pa>\n"
"I think only I call him that. <6.so>He runs the \n"
"<7.se_co>dye shop <8.re_co>near the bridge. He is WEIRD.<9.pa>\n"
"Yeah, his real name is Sayge, and he's\n"
"definitely a master of dyeing clothes, but<10.pa>\n"
"he's also a master of weirding me out."
msgstr ""

