msgctxt "talk13"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh, a very strange place, huh? <2.pa>\n"
"Only one place you could mean.\n"
"\n"
"The easternmost structure in this village,<3.pa>\n"
"at the top of the hill...<4.pa> Yup, you mean the\n"
"<5.se_co>Hateno Ancient Tech Lab<6.re_co>, right?\n"
"Its <7.se_co>director <8.re_co>does \"research\" there every\n"
"day, supposedly to help keep us all safe,\n"
"but who knows what THAT means!<9.pa>\n"
"That <10.se_co>director <11.re_co>doesn't like kids all that\n"
"much,<12.pa> so I hear the village tykes get\n"
"curious and snoop around a lot..."
msgstr ""

