msgid ""
"<1.so>If you want somewhere to rest, the <2.se_co>inn<3.re_co>\n"
"is the usual choice for travelers...<4.pa>\n"
"\n"
"<5.so>But maybe you mean...<6.pa>the model houses\n"
"<7.se_co>behind the general store<8.re_co>?<9.pa>\n"
"\n"
"Bolson Construction—yeah, they put \n"
"those up. Nice beds, OK furniture...<10.pa>\n"
"\n"
"<11.so>They've got that brand-new house smell.<12.pa>\n"
"Wouldn't mind sleeping in that smell\n"
"just once."
msgstr ""

